        </item>
        <item>
            <title>動物森友會 x LEGO 新產品登場　兩款場景包括服務處和機場</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 15:00:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LEGO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[動物森友會]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231847</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《動物森友會》幾年前曾經相當熱門，至今仍然有不少玩家。LEGO 在上月推出聯乘產品，最近再次公佈新作，包含兩款人氣遊戲場景。<br /><span id="more-1231847"></span></p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">🎵 K.K. is bringing some extra groove to the LEGO Animal Crossing range from August 1! <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/LEGO?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#LEGO</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/AnimalCrossing?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#AnimalCrossing</a><a href="https://t.co/R2uIW9lDIa">pic.twitter.com/R2uIW9lDIa</a></p><p>&mdash; LEGO (@LEGO_Group) <a href="https://twitter.com/LEGO_Group/status/1783858761444037049?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 26, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>LEGO 在 X 上公佈，將會在 8 月 1 日推出新的《動物森友會》場景套裝，包括有服務處和 Dodo 機場兩款，前者除了建築物之外，還會有小火車、美食攤以及 K.K. 演唱會舞台。組閤中除了 K.K. 外還會有西施惠和莫妮卡。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingto-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231848" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingto-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingto.jpg 791w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>至於機場套裝，則會有水上飛機和沙灘擺設，人物方面有陸德里和純純。不過暫時仍然未有例如套裝的實際積木數量以及價格等詳情，有興趣的朋友可以繼續留意一下。</p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingda-694x367.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="367" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231849" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingda-694x367.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingda.jpg 854w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>來源：<a href="https://jaysbrickblog.com/news/two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming-in-august-2024-including-a-kk-slider-minifigure/">Jay&#8217;s Brick Blog</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming/game-channel/">動物森友會 x LEGO 新產品登場　兩款場景包括服務處和機場</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
